description: Passengers will fall under "red" travel rules from midnight over concerns of a new Covid variant.
title: All UK arrivals in Jersey to require 10-day isolation
title_page: All UK arrivals in Jersey to require 10-day isolation - BBC News
maintext: The government said all eligible care home residents had received their first dose of the Pfizer/BioNTech vaccine, making Jersey "one of the first places in the world to vaccinate this group".
